<p itemprop="description">Technology strategy involves developing and implementing comprehensive plans for technology adoption, investment, and governance to support government objectives and digital transformation.</p>

<div class="proficiency-levels">
    <h2>Proficiency Levels</h2>

    <ol class="skill-levels">
        <li>
            <h3>Awareness</h3>
            <p>You can understand the importance of technology strategy and recognise how technology planning supports government service delivery and digital transformation.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Working</h3>
            <p>You can contribute to technology strategy development, understand technology trends, and align technology activities with organizational goals.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Practitioner</h3>
            <p>You can develop comprehensive technology strategies, create technology roadmaps, and establish frameworks for technology decision-making and governance.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Expert</h3>
            <p>You can lead enterprise technology strategy across government, influence technology policy, and drive organizational transformation through strategic technology initiatives.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>

